| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5118 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b0daef4b-9c8f-51d8-91ed-5e25c97e521c"
